Hey Sam,

Np! Once we were all knew to torrenting.

When you allow other people to download a file from your computer, you become a seeder for that file. When you are downloading a file from another computer, you become a leecher.

The more seeders, the greater the number of computers that have that file available for download. The more leechers, the greater the number of people trying to download that file.

When your download is finished, you automatically become a seeder, and people can download that file from your computer. In most cases people can also downloads parts of the file when you are still leeching (downloading) yourself.

Hope that helps!
